dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49	Woodland Meadows MHC	direct_syndication	raising_capital	506_b	2026-06-06	Woodland Meadows MHC LLC	t	t	Woodland Meadows Mobile Home Village	US	1431 Walnut St	\N	Cañon City	CO	81212	{}	2026-05-13 13:26:29.552703	2026-05-13 13:26:29.552703	deal-assets/dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49/screenshot-2026-05-13-at-8-36-36-am_36348f07-80c4-4ca6-9ada-5213f2d38249_1778679405748.png;deal-assets/dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49/screenshot-2026-05-13-at-8-37-29-am_fc22a198-4922-4e95-8905-32decf8deb56_1778681986386.png	fdb3343e-cf03-471b-bfb9-1a6ef904f056	<p>The community currently generates positive cash flow with meaningful upside remaining. Lot rents sit approximately $60 below market at $550/month, providing a clear, responsible path to value creation through gradual rent alignment.</p><p>Current lot rent includes water, sewer, and trash. A utility bill-back (individual water/sewer metering and per-tenant) will reduce operating expense and improve NOI.</p><p>On-site garage spaces will be converted to storage units at a projected $75/month each, adding a low-cost, high-margin revenue stream with minimal capital outlay.</p><p>The park is centrally located within Cañon City—walkable to shops, dining, and tourist attractions including the Royal Gorge Route Railroad and whitewater rafting. The area median home value is approximately $310,000, with two-bedroom apartments renting near $1,200/month, reinforcing the community's position as an affordable, stable housing alternative.</p><p>Employment in Fremont County is anchored by retail, hospitality, tourism, and stable public-sector jobs — including the Fremont County Detention Center and Colorado Department of Corrections facilities — supporting consistent housing demand.</p><p>Operational improvements include automated rent collection and resident communication software, already deployed at our other MHP assets. Our management approach prioritizes resident retention, curb appeal, and transparent communication as the foundation for sustainable value growth.</p>	https://syndicationx.com/uploads/deal-assets/dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49/screenshot-2026-05-13-at-8-36-36-am_36348f07-80c4-4ca6-9ada-5213f2d38249_1778679405748.png	[{"id":"preset-0","metric":"Annualized return","newClass":"26.51%","isPreset":true},{"id":"preset-1","metric":"Average cash-on-cash","newClass":"9%","isPreset":true},{"id":"preset-2","metric":"Equity multiple","newClass":"2.33","isPreset":true},{"id":"preset-3","metric":"IRR","newClass":"20.81%","isPreset":true},{"id":"preset-4","metric":"Holding period","newClass":"5 Years","isPreset":true}]	\N	\N	draft_hidden	show_on_dashboard	f		["primary-dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49"]	["deal-assets/dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49/screenshot-2026-05-13-at-8-36-36-am_36348f07-80c4-4ca6-9ada-5213f2d38249_1778679405748.png","deal-assets/dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49/screenshot-2026-05-13-at-8-37-29-am_fc22a198-4922-4e95-8905-32decf8deb56_1778681986386.png"]	_0jOcLntVUFai0Ut.Unbyb3wfdRnEofey73hwVA.Jatd0k-9SXFFSgfbRS9VRHKPn1o3hf67yTH6ecTLeQsbckQq	{"v":1,"visibility":{"make_announcement":true,"overview":true,"offering_information":true,"gallery":true,"summary":true,"documents":true,"assets":true,"key_highlights":true,"funding_instructions":true},"sections":[{"id":"section-1778789729035","sectionLabel":"Woodland Meadows MHC LLC Subscription Agreement 506b","documentLabel":"Woodland Meadows MHC LLC Subscription Agreement 506b","visibility":"Offering page","sharedWithScope":"offering_page","requireLpReview":false,"dateAdded":"14-May-2026","nestedDocuments":[{"id":"section-1778789729035-nest-0","name":"Woodland Meadows MHC LLC Subscription Agreement 506b 5.13.26.docx.pdf","url":"/uploads/deal-assets/dd9a2954-ed9a-494e-b488-474b57021a49/woodland-meadows-mhc-llc-subscription-agreement-506b-5-13-26-docx_1761d517-e079-43b1-ad9b-512829490eb5_1778789729783.pdf","dateAdded":"14-May-2026","lpDisplaySectionId":"section-1778789729035"}]}