5a8f9d0d-8fb4-4a5e-849f-981a647ba19a	Cash Flow Fund X	fund	raising_capital	506_b	2026-08-31	Pending	f	f	Pending	US	\N	\N	Pending	\N	\N	{}	2026-05-12 13:32:28.085181	2026-05-12 13:32:28.085181	deal-assets/5a8f9d0d-8fb4-4a5e-849f-981a647ba19a/massive-access-pic_22124765-6d4b-4d46-8be9-cab582342ee7_1779675982234.jpeg	af6822c5-3a6d-4ce4-8b1a-7b9baf481698	<p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," /></p><p></p><p><span style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">1.  Cashflow Fund X, an open-ended fund focused on providing </span><strong style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">equity to commercial real estate properties</strong><span style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">.</span></p><p></p><p><span style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">2. A dislocation in the capital markets has created a unique opportunity to provide capital </span><strong style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">through preferred equity and mezzanine debt</strong></p><p></p><p><span style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">3. This fund will be focused on providing </span><strong style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">current cash yield </strong><span style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">while investing in preferred positions in the underlying investment</span></p><p></p><p><span style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">4. Cash Flow fund strategy is founded on the belief that </span><strong style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">downside risk can be limited, and thus losses avoided</strong><span style="color:rgb(16, 46, 80)">, through two complementary approaches: rigorous credit analysis and active portfolio management</span></p><p></p><p><strong>Investment Objective</strong></p><p></p><p>Cashflow Fund X will invest in:</p><p>•Cash Flowing Commercial Properties</p><p>•Class A Retail Centers</p><p>•MHPs &amp; RV Parks</p><p>•Cashflowing Businesses</p><p>•Storage Facilities</p><p>•Residential Assisted Living</p><p>•Short Term High Yield Loans</p><p>•Liquid Assets While on Hold for Deals</p><p></p><p>Across sunbelt with heavy focus on Texas</p>	https://syndicationx.com/uploads/deal-assets/5a8f9d0d-8fb4-4a5e